    public class PaginatedList<T>
extends java.util.ArrayList<T>
    This class is a list impplementation, used to handle list of objects returned by Deezer API.

    When the total number of objects in a Deezer Request response is too large, Deezer API then limit results to a page, but provides the total number of elements in the query result, as well as the Deezer Request URL one can use to get the next and previous page.
